openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: These $refs in parameter examples should not be resolved
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /:
    parameters:
      - in: query
        name: param1
        schema:
          type: object
        example:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Foo'
          arr:
            - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Foo'
      - in: query
        name: param2
        schema:
          type: object
        examples:
          '0':
            value:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Foo'
              arr:
                - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Foo'
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: param3
          schema:
            type: object
          example:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Foo'
            arr:
              - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Foo'
        - in: query
          name: param4
          schema:
            type: object
          examples:
            '1':
              value:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Foo'
                arr:
                  - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Foo'
        - in: query
          name: param5
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                type: object
              example:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Foo'
                arr:
                  - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Foo'
        - in: query
          name: param6
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                type: object
              examples:
                '2':
                  value:
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/Foo'
                    arr:
                      - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Foo'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
components:
  schemas:
    Foo:
      type: string
